Hold it. What about my famous
Kung Pao lettuce wraps?

05:42.429 --> 05:44.387
You don't know about
those, do you? Yeah.

05:44.431 --> 05:45.867
Little Eastern medicine secret
I picked up

05:45.910 --> 05:47.216
while I was living in Beijing.

05:47.259 --> 05:49.044
Yeah, as a wise
village elder

05:49.087 --> 05:51.351
once said to me...
