11:25.293 --> 11:29.253
Oh, backhand down the line.

11:29.297 --> 11:31.560
No, it hit the net.

11:33.127 --> 11:34.868
Your mom went to serve,
then we got hit

11:34.911 --> 11:36.913
by the same wave
of food poisoning,

11:36.957 --> 11:39.742
all because we let this guy
take care of you.

11:39.786 --> 11:41.265
Okay, hold on, Dad.

11:41.309 --> 11:43.006
We can't blame all this on Jake.

11:43.050 --> 11:45.269
Oh, it had to be
those damn wraps.

11:45.313 --> 11:47.358
The only other food we had today

11:47.402 --> 11:51.145
were olives, two celery sticks
and an orange peel.

11:53.147 --> 11:55.105
So just cocktail
garnishes.

11:56.498 --> 11:58.674
You guys probably have
alcohol poisoning.

12:02.286 --> 12:03.766
I mean, how can germs
even survive

12:03.810 --> 12:06.464
in that duty-free store
you call a stomach?

12:06.508 --> 12:09.729
Then why is Cooper also sick?

12:09.772 --> 12:11.774
Sorry to miss the VMAs, guys,

12:11.818 --> 12:13.994
but, uh, I promise
I'll make it up to you all

12:14.037 --> 12:15.212
when I'm feeling better.

12:15.256 --> 12:17.432
Especially you, Lauren.

12:17.475 --> 12:18.781
Oh, who's Lauren?

12:18.825 --> 12:21.001
Don't know, but, uh,
12,000 girls named Lauren

12:21.044 --> 12:22.742
just swallowed their retainers.

12:24.787 --> 12:26.310
Great job, Jake.

12:26.354 --> 12:27.964
We leave you in charge
for one day

12:28.008 --> 12:29.792
and you poison
the whole family. You...

12:29.836 --> 12:32.534
You're like a villain
from Game of Thrones.

12:37.278 --> 12:40.368
Look, I am telling you,
this is all one big coincidence.

12:40.411 --> 12:42.196
Okay, so, you're telling me
you washed your hands

12:42.239 --> 12:43.327
before you started cooking?

12:43.371 --> 12:44.851
Yes, Gerald.

12:44.894 --> 12:46.983
And you cooked the chicken
all the way?

12:47.027 --> 12:49.551
Yes, Bonnie.

12:49.594 --> 12:51.422
And did you wash the lettuce?

12:51.466 --> 12:52.554
Y...

12:54.730 --> 12:58.821
Did I wash the lettuce?

12:58.865 --> 13:01.824
Did Iwash
the lettuce?

13:01.868 --> 13:05.088
